Package: mlds
Title: Explore the works of Marxist-Leninists via a Shiny app
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Alice Circe", "Malone", ,"circemalone@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This Shiny app allows users to query Marxist-Leninist texts for 
    keywords of interest, and provides relevant passages and word frequencies
    in the form of human-readable tables and graphs.
